### Risk Rating Key
* **Likelihood (L):** 1 (Unlikely) to 5 (Almost Certain)
* **Impact (I):** 1 (Insignificant) to 5 (Catastrophic)
* **Risk Score:** $\text{Likelihood} \times \text{Impact}$
  * 🔴 **High (15–25):** Active executive oversight & continuous mitigation required.
  * 🟡 **Medium (8–14):** Managed via operational controls & periodic monitoring.
  * 🟢 **Low (1–7):** Routine operational handling.
